# Library Website — Team Manifest
# v0.19.7 | 02 April 2026
#
# WARDLEY MAP LOGIC
# Explorer  (Genesis → Custom-Built)  → builds first version of the library
# Villager  (Custom-Built → Product)  → hardens and deploys to library.sgraph.ai
# Town Planner (Product → Commodity)  → drives adoption across all projects
#
# DEPENDENCY CHAIN: Explorer → Villager → Town Planner

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TEAM 1: Explorer — Library Build
# Lead: Librarian
# Center of gravity: "Scattered knowledge becomes a browsable, cloneable library.
#   Every agent session starts with full team context — no hunting, no re-reading.
#   Success: a new project can bootstrap its agentic team from one git clone."
# Focus: New repo creation, content migration, website, indexing
# Working files: explorer-library/
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

