# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TEAM 3: Town Planner — Cross-Project Adoption
# Lead: Conductor
# Center of gravity: "The library is only valuable when used. Every project
#   repo references it. Every new session starts from it. The SG/Send CLAUDE.md
#   becomes a thin wrapper around the library.
#   Success: spinning up a new project takes < 5 minutes using the library."
# Focus: Updating all project repos, reducing duplication, proving cross-project reuse
# Working files: town-planner-adoption/
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

